quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  24,54,"Maaku: \"∆äoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on\". Si …ďe huccitii(runtiima) anndu ko fawii mo ko, ko o roondaa kon, no fawii on ko roonda …óon kon, si on …óoftike mo on feeway, fawaaki Nulaa…óo on si wanaa yottinngol …ďanngungol"
  24,55,"Alla Fodii …ďen gom…óin…ďe e moo…óon …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin O lontinay …ďe ka leydi wano O lontinirnoo non …ďen adii…ďe …ďe, ma O wee…ďinan …ďe diina ma…ď…ďe ka O welanaa …ďe, ma O wattitan …ďe …ďaawo kulol ma…ď…ďe ngol hoolaare, Yo …ďe rewam wata …ďe sirkanam hay e huunde. Kala yeddu…óo …ďaawo …óum haray …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe woni faasiqii…ďe …ďen"
  24,56,"√Ďii…ďee e Julde totton Jakka on …óofto…óon kadi Nulaa…óo on, bela jo'o on Yurmete"
  24,57,"Wata a sikku …ďeen yeddu…ďe …ďe laawoto ka leydi, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko ka Yiite, pellet, bonii wattnde"
  24,58,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe, yo sakkintino e moo…óon …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon jeyi, e …ďen …ďe yottaaki koy…óol immorde e moo…óon, laabi tati ko adii Julde Peeral nden, e tuma wallinton conci moo…óon ka njolloro e ka …ďaawo Julde gee∆īe ko awraaji moo…óon tati non. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fawaaki …ďe …ďaawo majji, jinndoo…ďe hakkunde moo…óon, yoga e moo…óon e dow yoga. Ko wano nii Alla …ďanngini- rani on Aayeeje …óen Alla ko O Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
